        <item>
            <title>Xbox Series X 白色数码版推出，高层透露正开发下世代主机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/xbox-series-x-digital-version/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xbox-series-x-digital-version</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/xbox-series-x-digital-version/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:30:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Xbox Series X]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241848</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 juice:w-full juice:items-end overflow-x-auto gap-2" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="bf968b1d-82d5-4024-a64d-3853a87bc2bd"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 juice:empty:hidden juice:first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>Microsoft 宣布将于 2024 年的假期季节推出数款全新 Xbox Series X 和 Xbox Series S 型号。这些新产品包括无光碟版的 Xbox Series X、特别版的 Xbox Series X 以及升级版 Xbox Series S，为玩家提供更多选择。</p></div></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 juice:empty:hidden juice:first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>新产品包括容量扩充至 2TB 并采用黑色外观的特别版 Xbox Series X「Galaxy Black」，该版本定价为 599.99 美元（约港币 46,800 元）。此外还有一款 1TB 的白色 Xbox Series X 无光碟版，定价为 449.99 美元（约港币 35,100 元）。另外，Xbox Series S 也推出了容量提升至 1TB 的新版本，售价为 349.99 美元（约港币 27,300 元）。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 juice:w-full juice:items-end overflow-x-auto gap-2" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="bf968b1d-82d5-4024-a64d-3853a87bc2bd"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 juice:empty:hidden juice:first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>Microsoft 表示上述新产品将于 2024 年的假期季节正式推出。除了硬体更新，Microsoft 也强调了其在保存游戏和上位兼容性方面的投入，并设立了一个专门的团队来支持这些工作。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_48873"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mzDPNi77F24?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Xbox 部门负责人 Sarah Bond 在 Xbox Games Showcase 上表示：「我们的目标是通过在 Xbox Game Pass 中添加更多自家工作室的游戏，将 Xbox 创造成最佳游戏平台。我们也在积极开发次世代硬件，期望能达到前所未有的技术突破。」</p><p>Bond 指出，Xbox 团队的使命是确保新产品在技术上有显著提升，同时也能提供更好的用户体验，满足玩家不断变化的需求。这次推出的新型号和更新的硬件配置，正是 Microsoft 朝这个目标迈进的重要一步。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center pb-0.5 juice:pb-0"></div><div></div><div><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/threenewxboxseriesx_-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/threenewxboxseriesx_-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/threenewxboxseriesx_-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><div>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/9/24174793/microsoft-xbox-series-x-white-digital-edition">The Verge</a></div><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/vladimir-putin-pushes-russia-to-make-consoles-to-compete-with-playstation-and-xbox/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">俄罗斯普京促自主研发游戏机　要能够与 PS5、Xbox Series X|S 抗衡</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/29/xbox-series-x-leak-white-all-digital/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新主机谍照网上流传，纯白色 Xbox Series X 数码版曝光</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/xbox-series-x-digital-version/game-channel/">Xbox Series X 白色数码版推出，高层透露正开发下世代主机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
